      "comment": "ZIPPING ARVADA (6) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that posted a lightning 22.29 win over 400m at Warragul. Has the ability and expected to go close again. LAURISTON GIRL (3) was below best at her last start when 8th at this track following a win (22.01) there two back. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Can do much better this time. WAXING (1) was a last start winner (17.08) at Healesville who is building a strong winning record. Has a good record here including two wins. Leading player again. ONE LAST BEER (4) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
